stories.title: Brett Lee gets his smile back
stories.subTitle: Australia v India, 11th ODI, VB Series, Perth
stories.summary: On a playing surface that suits their full-throttle style more than most, Australia's batsmen and bowlers came into their own, with Brett Lee hauling himself into the light after a doom-and-gloom summer
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Dileep Premachandran
